DATA ATTRIBUTION

Financial data used in this portfolio originates from the following
official public sources and is used exclusively for educational and
portfolio demonstration purposes:

  - SEC EDGAR (U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission)
    https://efts.sec.gov

  - Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED), St. Louis Fed
    https://fred.stlouisfed.org

  - World Bank Open Data
    https://data.worldbank.org

  - International Monetary Fund (IMF) Data
    https://www.imf.org/en/Data

  - Nairobi Securities Exchange (NSE)
    https://www.nse.co.ke

  - London Stock Exchange (LSE)
    https://www.londonstockexchange.com

  - NYSE / NASDAQ (via Yahoo Finance public API)
    https://finance.yahoo.com

  - Central Bank of Kenya (CBK)
    https://www.centralbank.go.ke

No proprietary, licensed, or confidential data has been used.
All figures in the dataset are either directly sourced from public
disclosures or are synthetic values generated for illustrative purposes.
